description.narrative: The Programme contributed to the Common Country Analysis developed ahead of the formulation of the new United Nations Sustainable Development Co-operation Framework (UNSDCF) for Cameroon. Dialogue with the Government and other key stakeholders (UNHCR, Plan International, UNESCO) at national and regional levels was continued. UNICEF provided multiform support in the revision process and successfully brought to the front the issue of inclusive education as a priority in the Education Sector Plan for 2020-2030. As sector lead of the Local Education in Emergencies Group, UNICEF technical coordinated the sector's COVID-19 response and leveraged USD 11 million from GPE. | Status:On-track | As-of Date:30/06/2020
